        time: - Time Format: hh-mm
        emotion: - List of Emotion: Sad, Happy, Boring, Anxious, Fearful, Angry
        reason: - A string to explain your emotion. Should be no more than 20 chars or 3 words.
        socialSituation: - There are 3 social situation: alone, with one other person, with two to several people, or with a crowd
        latitude: - a google map data type to indicate where the user is when he/she upload a new mood event.
